    <item>
      <title>土耳其警察拘留Erdogan竞争对手Ekrem Imamoglu</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/turkish-police-detains-erdogan-rival-ekrem-imamoglu</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据Cnnturk说，伊斯坦布尔市长埃克雷姆·伊玛莫格鲁（Ekrem Imamoglu）周三早上被拘留在他的家中，这是在土耳其当局撤销大学文凭的第二天。这一举动可以使他不得在下次总统大选中挑战Recep Tayyip Erdogan。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/turkish-police-detains-erdogan-rival-ekrem-imamoglu</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Mar 2025 04:52:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普批准Venture Global的CP2项目的LNG出口</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/trump-to-approve-lng-exports-from-venture-global-s-cp2-project</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特朗普政府准备给予Venture Global Lng Inc.有条件地批准，以从计划中的一家计划中的设施出口天然气，该设施在前总统乔·拜登（Joe Biden）的带领下停滞不前。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/trump-to-approve-lng-exports-from-venture-global-s-cp2-project</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Mar 2025 04:29:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普说我们不希望俄罗斯，中国一起移动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/trump-says-us-doesn-t-want-russia-china-moving-closer-together</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统对中国和俄罗斯之间更紧密的联系表示谨慎，概述了与两个国家在世界舞台上反对美国的关系的计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/trump-says-us-doesn-t-want-russia-china-moving-closer-together</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Mar 2025 02:48:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哥伦比亚财务负责人辞职，确认投资者担心</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/colombia-s-finance-chief-resigns-confirming-investor-fears</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哥伦比亚财政部长迭戈·格瓦拉（Diego Guevara）证实了较早的新闻报道，他在任职仅三个月后就提交了辞职，这一举动使该国的资产于周二大跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/colombia-s-finance-chief-resigns-confirming-investor-fears</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Mar 2025 02:36:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管公众反弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/indonesia-fast-tracks-military-changes-despite-public-backlash</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印尼立法者正在迅速通过一项有争议的法案，该法案将扩大军队的作用，即使公众批评的变化让人联想到东南亚国家的专制过去。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/indonesia-fast-tracks-military-changes-despite-public-backlash</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Mar 2025 01:24:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>国土安全部削减了与国内极端主义斗争的人员</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/dhs-slashes-personnel-leading-fight-against-domestic-extremism</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据现任和前官员的说法，特朗普政府对美国政府工人的清除局势摧毁了一个旨在打击在线激进化的国土安全部门，并认为在过去几年中有助于破坏1000多个暴力地块。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/dhs-slashes-personnel-leading-fight-against-domestic-extremism</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Mar 2025 01:21:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普说，与加拿大的自由领导人打交道会更容易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/trump-on-canada-elections-it-ll-be-easier-to-deal-with-liberal-leader</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）表示，他宁愿与加拿大的自由党领导人合作，以解决他与渥太华煽动的贸易战，并权衡了邻国北美国家的一次预期民族大选。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/trump-on-canada-elections-it-ll-be-easier-to-deal-with-liberal-leader</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Mar 2025 01:12:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>普京拒绝了乌克兰停火，但特朗普称谈话胜利</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/putin-spurns-ukraine-ceasefire-in-talks-but-trump-calls-it-a-win</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统弗拉基米尔·普京（Vladimir Putin）拒绝让唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）在乌克兰的30天停火中，他和他的团队要求在结束三年冲突的道路上。对于美国总统来说，这仍然足够好。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/putin-spurns-ukraine-ceasefire-in-talks-but-trump-calls-it-a-win</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Mar 2025 01:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
